{
  "_comment": "Friendly names for AFMER fields. Read by `afmer-etl --export-json` and embedded into the SPA's data/meta.json (as `labels`), where the SPA shows them for column headers, the metric picker, and summary cards. Edit the `name` of any entry to change how it appears; `group`/`activity`/`caliber` are optional extras you can use for grouping in reports. Keys are the data column codes and must not change. Codes not listed here fall back to the raw code.",
